# {{.Type}}: {{.Name}}

{{ .Description | trimspace }}

Use this data source to reference an existing Kosli service account and access its metadata, such as the granted privilege, the creating user, and the creation timestamp.

## Example Usage

{{tffile "examples/data-sources/kosli_service_account/data-source.tf"}}

## Read-Only Access

Data sources provide read-only access to service account metadata. To create or modify service accounts, use the `kosli_service_account` resource. To manage API keys, use the `kosli_service_account_api_key` resource.

